      "dc:title": "ERDERA Metric - R1.3 - Metadata - Metadata meets minimal VP Metadata for ERDERA Virtual Platform Level 2 Compliance  ",
      "http://vivoweb.org/ontology/core#abbreviation": "FM_R1-3_M_VP_L2",
      "dcat:landingPage": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/fair-metrics/erdera/FM_R1-3_M_VP_L2"
      },
      "dc:description": "\n                           The ERDERA Project has strict requirements for minimal metadata to onboard their Virtual Platform. \n                            For Level 2, you must first be Level 1 compliant (see https://w3id.org/fair-metrics/erdera/FM_R1-3_M_VP_L1).\n                            In addition, you must declare yourself as a dcat Data Service, and have a landingPage at a minimimum.\n\n",
